data.description: Welcome to your dream lakefront retreat at Sebastian Cove! This impressive architecturally designed home offers the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and breathtaking views. This residence boasts spacious living areas and is thoughtfully designed to accommodate two additional bedrooms on the lake level.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of oak hardwood floors throughout the main level and the luxurious master bedroom on level three. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertaining. Natural light floods the interior, highlighting the attention to detail and craftsmanship.  Indulge in the stunning views from the lakeside screen porch, accessible from the lakeside deck. Enjoy your morning coffee while listening to the gentle lapping of the water, or host unforgettable gatherings against the backdrop of the expansive open lake view.  The home's exterior features a timeless blend of Hardie Board and stone, ensuring durability and low maintenance for years to come. With 2-inch by 6-inch stud exterior insulated walls, this home offers high energy efficiency, providing comfort in every season. Each level has its own individual HVAC system, allowing personalized climate control throughout.  Immerse yourself in the beautifully landscaped surroundings, complete with specimen mature trees, shrubs, and ground cover. The Zoysia grass lawn is meticulously maintained by the lake-fed irrigation system, creating a lush and vibrant outdoor space.  Sebastian Cove is not only renowned for its stunning lakefront properties but also offers a range of amenities. Residents have access to a private air strip, tennis courts, walking trails, a boat ramp, and a clubhouse. Experience the ultimate lakefront lifestyle with 4 to 5 feet of water depth at the flag dock, perfect for boating and water activities. Georgia Power has approved the addition of a boat lift at the dock.  This exceptional property spans an impressive 5,400 square feet, with 4,145 square feet heated and cooled. The current owners have spared no expense in creating a residence that exemplifies luxury lakefront living.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this exquisite lakefront retreat at Sebastian Cove. Schedule your private viewing today and let this stunning property become your own lakeside paradise.
